channel.name: wip
channel.topic: A place to see exclusive subscriber-only content first such as works in progress, teaser videos, and more!

messages.content: Hello, everyone and welcome to our Exclusive-Pro-Subscriber-Only-Amazing-Content-With-Awesome-Things Channel! We'll post extra content here, first-first looks, and more. You are not required to keep this content a secret from the world. Stay tuned for our first drop. 🥳
Here are some new angles at LFBO for you! Our airport editors are amazing.

As is our new custom, you folks get a little extra from what is shown on social media! No need to keep this private so share away! Here we have the high-polygon rendering as well as two never before seen wireframes of the nose gear and cabin on the E175!

Coming to 22.3! Here are a few extra angles for you. This tug is currently set to handle smaller airliners around 100,000kg MTO and under, although Laura tells me there could be some exceptions based on fit.
@🔔 WIP Check out what we're talking about in the pilot lounge stage right now!
E175 3D wireframe rendering in high poly. 😍
@🔔 WIP here is the subscriber only shot that @9to5Gamer and @Owen ✈ were too impatient to wait for :Troll: Enjoy.
Oh hello, ground ops! Did anyone order the kosher meal?
Oops... forgot the 🔔. Hello @🔔 WIP ☝️
Good morning @🔔 WIP people! Happy Friday.
@🔔 WIP taxiway lights 😱
@🔔 WIP As is our new custom, you folks get an extra sneaky peek at the latest social media shot!
@🔔 WIP Here are some more Tug angles for your Friday! We're super thankful for our friends at Best Tugs for allowing us to feature their awesome products in the sim! #backtowork 🤠
@🔔 WIP  A new 3D airport spinning it's way into 22.4! Can you guess which one?
Started a thread.
Taxiway lighting WIP coming up later today 👀
@🔔 WIP Here are the official social media images, along with an extra one from me, and an extra from Laura (from the cockpit) during development. Enjoy!

@🔔 WIP 

Kilimanjaro International (HTKJ) will be joining the lineup of 3D airports in 22.4! With connecting flights to many of our African 3D airports, you can catch a glimpse of the famous Mount Kilimanjaro whether you're coming or going. 🏔️
@🔔 WIP  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bkn7OIvG0Nc

embeds.title: Ground Service Equipment
embeds.description:
Coming soon to Infinite Flight 22.4 is Ground Service Equipment! For many flight sim enthusiasts, the ground experience can be just as important as the one in the air. Here's a first look at what's coming to improve your ground ops in Infinite Flight. 

Disclaimer: This feature is a work in progress and subject to change. Footage in development ...

messages.content:
**E175 Cockpit and Exterior Models** 
Our E175 cockpit is being finalized, and the exterior model is having textures and ambient occlusion applied. The aircraft will soon be handed over to developers who will bring it to life!
@🔔 WIP
I don't have another wingtip angle for you from today's social media WIP so here's one I can't explain very well. We'll just call it the E175 ghost. 👻  @🔔 WIP

:mic: **Calling all cargo haulers!**

 📦 🇧🇷 📦 @🔔 WIP 📦 🇧🇷 📦

22.4 will include Campinas International (SBKP) which is the second busiest cargo airport in Brazil. SBKP offers many exciting routes with Azul and GOL along with an impressive cargo network reaching classic airports all over the Americas, Europe, and Africa!

🐝 Development has resumed and artists are preparing the Super Hornet for textures! @🔔 WIP 
PLEASE NOTE: THERE IS NO RELEASE DATE OR VERSION SET FOR THIS AIRCRAFT.
Happy Thursday @🔔 WIP group! Here's a close-up chunk of the main wheel well, which is integrated into the wing box fairing. This is a low-poly model rendering from E175 exterior development.
Happy hump day, Pro Subscribers! Thank you for spending your hard-earned cash with us. Here's a @🔔 WIP photo dump from the development archive never shared. You're going to love the final product!
Happy E175 @🔔 WIP day! Also happy America day to our US friends. 🦅
Happy hump day, friends. @🔔 WIP

We hope to have this airplane and the F18 at Oshkosh in a week and a half. They might not be full versions (still waiting on exterior model for Jarno to start liveries) but something that flies and is okay for a demo. So you'll likely see lots of leaks starting in a few weeks! 
FAQ for the thread above:
- There is no set release date for this or the F18
- The fact that it's demo'd at OSH does not imply isn't released in 22.6

Happy friday, @🔔 WIP people! Will the F18 have afterburner? Yes. Yes it will. 
As with the EJet, we hope to showcase the F18 at Oshkosh in a little over a week. This does not imply a 22.6 release.

More #ThursdayVibes coming at you courtesy of Laura! @🔔 WIP 
PLEASE NOTE that we are aware there is no over-wing door on the E-175 and it will be removed before going to production. We're also aware this shot doesn't include textured pilots. We, of course, will not release that way. All work-in-progress shots are subject to approval. 
Enjoy!
Hey @🔔 WIP, we released this on social media today! Let me know what you want to see from the F18 in the thread below and we'll select one of the requests to show you right here!
Here's a @🔔 WIP shot of the AeroMexico 738 coming to 22.6!
Check out this @🔔 WIP of the Kuwait Air Force F/A-18E joining the Infinite Flight fleet! 🇰🇼
Happy Friday, @🔔 WIP! Here's another angle of the E175 on the maintenance ramp. Can't wait to get this beauty into the air!
Excuse me @🔔 WIP but would anyone like to see these screens turn on? 👀

Here's a quick zoom around the Alaska Airlines E175 for today's @🔔 WIP! Beta testing is rolling along and we're getting really excited to share this beauty with all of you! 
Thanks for being Infinite Flight Pro subscribers!
You voted, and now new custom tower models are coming to VHHH! @🔔 WIP

Hello @🔔 WIP folks! It's our pleasure to present the finished product from our E175 livery contest! @Samirrrrrr did an amazing job designing this livery and our 3D artists have delivered! Here is the artist 3D rendering and the corresponding in-app version which is now available to our beta testing team.
Here’s a double @🔔 WIP shot in one photo! KORD is making steady progress and it will ship with **4 custom towers**! 👀 Oh yeah, there’s the E175 too. Almost forgot about that one 😅
It's a good day for a @🔔 WIP landing video! 📽️  Any flybe fans out there?
Sorry about the file download folks. I must have hit some sort of file extension or size limit. Here's something a little more user friendly. https://vimeo.com/infiniteflight/e175-flybe-landing
